--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README : LiBiNorm
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LiBiNorm has been designed to perform gene expression analysis using RNA-seq data. 
It is command line and output compatible with htseq-count and also includes RNA-seq 
bias compensation tailored to library preparation as described in the paper: 
Modeling enzyme processivity reveals that RNA-Seq libraries are biased in 
characteristic and correctable ways
http://www.cell.com/cell-systems/fulltext/S2405-4712(16)30331-3

